name: Where To? (Narsiph)
description:
Where To?

You have to deal with a lot of weirdos that dont even bother to tell you which floor they want to go. But, you're a good liftboy and you always know where they want to go to.

Do you?

Test your movie-knowledge in this one button quiz-elevator game. This is a game-jam game.

Programming: Narsiph

2D-Assets: Luziferattus
